  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      This is a multicenter, randomized, double-blind, placebo-controlled study on the
      effectiveness of treatment with beta-blockers to prevent decompensation of cirrhosis with
      portal hypertension.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
